{"tid":1650040,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"嬲還嬲 場仗唔可以就咁完","createTime":"2019-10-12T19:52:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-13T05:50:14.000Z","uid":66577,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"19d1b39f87490588ff5efc5f5796bf5a5c249dc5","tid":1650040,"uid":66577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:52:10.000Z","msg":"香港人由加油進化到反抗用左四個月時間<br />\n我地先岩岩開始行出第一步<br />\n唔好俾啲尻人阻到我地腳步<br />\n我都好嬲 特別係我今日先經過嗰到<br />\n但我唔會就咁放棄<br />\n<br />\n如果就咁放棄我地點對得住<br />\n以死明志、被魔警濫捕甚至謀殺嘅手足？<br />\n<br />\n記住呢句<br />\n懇請不要被仇恨蒙蔽雙眼<br />\n<br />\n無論班扮黃拎光環嘅撚樣同魔警點都媽，我地幾憤怒都好，我地都唔好放棄"},{"pid":"a510e563e210bd9954db63ee4a63cb28cd0c2484","tid":1650040,"uid":325269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:53:50.000Z","msg":"不篤灰 不割蓆唔係口號<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71rUgoF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71rUgoF.jpg&h=dfc19a1d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AmG1FQk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAmG1FQk.jpg&h=16c44ce3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Jk7sBoG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJk7sBoG.png&h=6f2b4d34&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Oue6RW2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOue6RW2.jpg&h=f95c8cc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c85025f3459c1d85508205d642c0f415f06db2e8","tid":1650040,"uid":549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-12T19:54:04.000Z","msg":"大家都知依場仗唔可以就咁完<br />\n努力啲推行動POST<br />\n唔好再開POST講大家都有共識既野<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0755233b04a466e526459bf84bdfeb9f927bc949